cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY. 

The paper deals with reinforcement learning of active vision for manipulating objects, which involves robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. The use of artificial agents and actor-critic architectures suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The coordination of camera and gripper control also implies a systems and control (cs.SY) aspect.
